#. Tag: title
#: installoshowto.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "How-To: Installing a New Operating System"
msgstr "Navodila: Namestitev novega operacijskega sistema"

#. Tag: para
#: installoshowto.docbook:4
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This how-to describes the preparation of a new hard disk device for an OS "
"installation: Suppose you bought a new hard disk and now intend to use it as "
"a replacement for the old one that currently holds your OS and data "
"partitions. You would also like to take this opportunity to install a new "
"operating system. Several steps will have to be taken to make the transition "
"from the old to the new system and drive."
msgstr ""
"Ta navodila opisujejo pripravo novega trdega diska za namestitev "
"operacijskega sistema (OS): Recimo, da ste kupili nov trdi disk in ga zdaj "
"nameravate uporabiti kot zamenjavo za starega, ki trenutno vsebuje vaš OS in "
"podatkovne particije. To priložnost bi radi izkoristili tudi za namestitev "
"novega operacijskega sistema. Za prehod s starega na nov sistem in pogon bo "
"treba narediti več korakov."

#. Tag: para
#: installoshowto.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the following, <quote>/dev/sdb</quote> is the old hard disk and <quote>/"
"dev/sdc</quote> is the new one. This screenshot shows the situation on the "
"source device:"
msgstr ""
"V nadaljevanju je <quote>/dev/sdb</quote> stari trdi disk, <quote>/dev/sdc</"
"quote> pa novi. Ta posnetek zaslona prikazuje stanje na izvorni napravi:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: installoshowto.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main window with source device"
msgstr "Glavno okno z izvorno napravo"

#. Tag: para
#: installoshowto.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The new device will look like this. Note that it doesn't yet have valid "
"partition table, thus the first step to take is to create one by selecting "
"<xref linkend=\"menu-device-createpartitiontable\"/>:"
msgstr ""
"Nova naprava bo videti takole. Upoštevajte, da še nima veljavne tabele "
"particij, zato je prvi korak, da jo ustvarite tako, da izberete <xref "
"linkend=\"menu-device-createpartitiontable\"/>:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: installoshowto.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main window with destination device"
msgstr "Glavno okno s ciljno napravo"

#. Tag: para
#: installoshowto.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After confirming the warning dialog you can begin creating partitions on the "
"new device by clicking the extended partition and selecting <xref linkend="
"\"menu-partition-new\"/>. Begin with an extended partition at the end of the "
"device to later hold the home and swap partitions:"
msgstr ""
"Ko potrdite opozorilno pogovorno okno, lahko začnete ustvarjati particije na "
"novi napravi, tako da kliknete razširjeno particijo in izberete <xref "
"linkend=\"menu-partition-new\"/>. Začnite z razširjeno particijo na koncu "
"naprave, da pozneje zadržite domačo in izmenjalno particijo:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: installoshowto.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating an extended partition"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje razširjene particije"

#. Tag: para
#: installoshowto.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click <guibutton>OK</guibutton> and the operation to create this extended "
"partition is added to the list."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton> in operacija za ustvarjanje te "
"razširjene particije bo dodana na seznam."

#. Tag: para
#: installoshowto.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now create a primary partition on the rest of the device where the new OS "
"will be installed. Make it as large as the unallocated area in front of the "
"extended partition:"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj ustvarite primarno particijo na preostalem delu naprave, kjer bo "
"nameščen nov OS. Velikost naj bo enaka nedodeljenemu območju pred razširjeno "
"particijo:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: installoshowto.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a primary partition"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje primarne particije"

#. Tag: para
#: installoshowto.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click <guibutton>OK</guibutton> in the dialog to accept your choice. The "
"operation to create the new primary partition is then added to the operation "
"list."
msgstr ""
"V pogovornem oknu kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, da sprejmete svojo "
"izbiro. Operacija za ustvarjanje nove primarne particije je nato dodana na "
"seznam operacij."

#. Tag: para
#: installoshowto.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now it is time to copy the home partition from the old device to the "
"extended partition on the new device. Select the old device in the Device "
"List panel, click on partition <quote>sdb5</quote> and pick <xref linkend="
"\"menu-partition-copy\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj je čas, da kopirate domačo particijo iz stare naprave v razširjeno "
"particijo na novi napravi. Na plošči Seznam naprav izberite staro napravo, "
"kliknite particijo <quote>sdb5</quote> in izberite <xref linkend=\"menu-"
"partition-copy\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: installoshowto.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Then go back to the new device and click the extended partition. Select "
"<xref linkend=\"menu-partition-paste\"/>. The following dialog will come up:"
msgstr ""
"Nato se vrnite na novo napravo in kliknite razširjeno particijo. Izberite "
"<xref linkend=\"menu-partition-paste\"/>. Prikaže se naslednje pogovorno "
"okno:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: installoshowto.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pasting the home partition"
msgstr "Lepljenje domače particije"

#. Tag: para
#: installoshowto.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This already looks mostly okay but you already know that you will not need "
"that much free space after the home partition because you will later create "
"a swap partition there."
msgstr ""
"To je že videti večinoma v redu, vendar že veste, da ne boste potrebovali "
"toliko prostega prostora po domači particiji, ker boste pozneje tam "
"ustvarili izmenjalno particijo."

#. Tag: para
#: installoshowto.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"So grab the right resize handle in the dialog's resizer widget and move it "
"to the right until the free space after the pasted partition has a size more "
"suitable for a swap partition:"
msgstr ""
"Zato zgrabite desno ročico za spreminjanje velikosti v pripomočku za "
"spreminjanje velikosti v pogovornem oknu in jo premikajte v desno, dokler "
"prosti prostor po prilepljeni particiji nima velikosti, ki je primernejša za "
"izmenjalno particijo:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: installoshowto.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resizing a pasted partition"
msgstr "Spreminjanje velikosti prilepljene particije"

#. Tag: para
#: installoshowto.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This looks fine. Click <guibutton>OK</guibutton> to accept and close the "
"dialog. A new operation to paste the copied partition to the extended "
"partition on <quote>sdc</quote> is added to the operation list. Note that "
"this operation will also set the new size."
msgstr ""
"To je videti v redu. Kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, da sprejmete in "
"zaprete pogovorno okno. Na seznam operacij je dodana nova operacija za "
"lepljenje kopirane particije v razširjeno particijo na <quote>sdc</quote>. "
"Upoštevajte, da bo ta operacija nastavila tudi novo velikost."

#. Tag: para
#: installoshowto.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally you will want to create a new swap partition at the end of the "
"extended partition on <quote>sdc</quote>. There is no need to copy the "
"existing swap partition from <quote>sdb</quote> because swap does not hold "
"any permanent information worth keeping. Simply create a new partition with "
"type linuxswap that fills the whole of the unallocated area after the new "
"home partition."
msgstr ""
"Na koncu boste želeli ustvariti novo izmenjalno particijo na koncu "
"razširjene particije na <quote>sdc</quote>. Obstoječe izmenjalne particije "
"ni treba kopirati iz <quote>sdb</quote>, ker izmenjalna particija (swap) ne "
"vsebuje trajnih informacij, ki bi jih bilo vredno obdržati. Preprosto "
"ustvarite novo particijo z vrsto linuxswap, ki zapolni celotno nedodeljeno "
"območje za novo domačo particijo."

#. Tag: para
#: installoshowto.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main window with all operations and the preview of how <quote>sdc</"
"quote> will look like once they are applied now looks like this:"
msgstr ""
"Glavno okno z vsemi operacijami in predogledom, kako bo <quote>sdc</quote> "
"izgledal, ko bodo uporabljene, je zdaj videti takole:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: installoshowto.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main window after setting up all operations"
msgstr "Glavno okno po nastavitvi vseh operacij"

#. Tag: para
#: installoshowto.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This looks great so select <xref linkend=\"menu-edit-apply\"/>, confirm the "
"warning dialog and wait until the operations have all been executed. For "
"details on executing operations see <link linkend=\"howto-resizepartition"
"\">the how-to on resizing partitions</link>."
msgstr ""
"To je videti odlično, zato izberite <xref linkend=\"menu-edit-apply\"/>, "
"potrdite opozorilno pogovorno okno in počakajte, da se izvedejo vse "
"operacije. Za podrobnosti o izvajanju operacij glejte <link linkend=\"howto-"
"resizepartition\">navodila za spreminjanje velikosti particij</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: installoshowto.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your new hard disk device is now ready for the installation of your new "
"operating system."
msgstr ""
"Vaš novi trdi disk je zdaj pripravljen za namestitev vašega novega "
"operacijskega sistema."
